. di _newline "--- Wald test with robust SEs ---"

--- Wald test with robust SEs ---

. quietly regress trade_balance t d2020 t_d2020, vce(robust)

. test d2020 t_d2020

 ( 1)  d2020 = 0
 ( 2)  t_d2020 = 0

       F(  2,     6) =    8.28
            Prob > F =    0.0188

. 
. drop d2020 t_d2020

